yeah     [A]  [D]  [A]   [E]\n\n[A]Let[D] me [A]tel[Dsus2]l you [A]all about it\n[A]   [A]   [Dsus2]      [A]\n\nI took her [A]home, to [D]my [A]place;\n[Dsus2]watching ev'ry [D]move on her [A]face,\nShe said [A]look, what's your [D]game, [A]\n[Dsus2]are you tryin' to [D]put me in [A]shame?\n\nBaby, I said [A]slow, [D]don't go so [A]fast,\n[Dsus2]don't you think that [D]love can [A]last?\nShe said [A]love, [D]Lord a[A]bove,\n[Dsus2]now you're tryin' to [D]trick me in l[A]ove.\n\n[A]All [D]right [A]now, baby, it's [G]all [D]right [A]now\n[A]All [D]right [A]now, baby, it's [G]all [D]right [A]now.  3x\n\nWe're so happy together, it's alright, it's alright..\n\nSet8\n","hash":"e1e0f95451b5cc81aee491159d8df3a5","key":0,"KeyShift":0,"name":"All Right Now","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-07-30T20:42:58.416700Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"8197b67e-d15a-4668-a3f3-418e253d03e9","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"all right now\nfree\nthere she stood in the street\narn\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":168,"author":"ZZ Top","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro/Riff}\n[F5]   [Eb5]    [C5]   [F5]   [Eb5]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\n[Cm]   Clean shirt, new shoes,\n[Bb]   And I don't know where I am g[F]oin' to.\n[Cm]   Silk suit, black tie,\n[Bb]   I don't need a reason [F]why.\n[G]   They come runnin' just as fast as they can,\nCoz [Cm]every girl crazy 'bout a sharp dressed man.\n\n{c: Riff}\n*\n[F5]   [Eb5]    [C5]   [F5]   [Eb5]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\n[Cm]   Gold watch, diamond ring,\n[Bb]   I ain't missin' not a [F]single thing.\n[Cm]   And cufflinks, stick pin,\n[Bb]   When I step out I'm gonna [F]do you in.\n[G]   They come runnin' just as fast as they can,\nCoz [Cm]every girl crazy 'bout a sharp dressed man.\n\n{c: Solo}\n[C5  (19 bars)]               [C5]   [Bb5]     [G5]\n[F]     [F]     [C5]     [C5]\n[F]     [F]     [C5]     [C5]   [Bb5]     [G5]\n\n{c: Riff}\n[F5]   [Eb5]    [C5]   [F5]   [Eb5]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[Cm]   Top coat, top hat,\n[Bb]   I don't worry coz my [F]wallet's fat.\n[Cm]   Black shades, white gloves,\n[Bb]   Lookin' sharp and [F]lookin' for love.\n[G]   They come runnin' just as fast as they can,\nCoz [Cm]every girl crazy 'bout a sharp dressed man.\n\n{c: Solo}\nC5  (20 bars)\n[F5]     [F5]     [F5]     [F5]\n[C5]     [C5]     [C5]     [Bb5]\n[F5]     [F5]     [F5]     [F5]\n[C5]     [C5]     [C5]     [C5]\n[F5]     [F5]     [F5]     [F5]\n[C5](fade[C5] out)[C5]\n","hash":"2c26ebbd552a397d1a7cc5ff286ead1d","key":8,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Sharp Dressed Man","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-07-30T20:43:57.453398Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"0825bd22-230e-4e16-88db-43d8e4804ff4","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"sharp dressed man\nzz top\nclean shirt new shoes\nsdm\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":169,"author":"Melissa Etheridge","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n[G]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\n[G]Please baby can't you see, my mind's a burnin' hell\nI got razors a rippin' and tearin' and strippin'\nMy heart apart as well\nTonight you told me, that you ache for something new\nAnd some other woman is lookin' like something\nThat might be good for you\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[Am]Go on and hold her till the [D]screaming is [D]go[Dsus4]ne    [D]\n[Am]Go on believe her when she te[D]lls you n[D]othing'[Dsus4]s wron[D]g\n[G]I'm the only one, who'll w[F]alk across the fire for y[Em]ou\n[G]I'm the only one, who'll d[F]rown in my desire for y[Em]ou\n[Am]It's only fear that makes you run, the [Cadd9]demons that you're hiding from\nWhen a[F]ll your promises are [Cadd9]gone, I'm the only o[G]ne...\n\n{c: Verse 2}\n[G]Please baby can't you see, I'm trying to explain\nI've been here before and I'm locking the door\nAnd I'm not going back again\nHer eyes and arms and skin won't make it go away\nYou'll wake up tomorrow and wrestle the sorrow\nThat holds you down today\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[Am]Go on and hold her till the [D]screaming is [D]go[Dsus4]ne    [D]\n[Am]Go on believe her when she te[D]lls you n[D]othing'[Dsus4]s wron[D]g\n[G]But I'm the only one, who'll w[F]alk across the fire for y[Em]ou\n[G]And I'm the only one, who'll d[F]rown in my desire for [Em]you\n[Am]It's only fear that makes you run, the [Cadd9]demons that you're hiding from\nWhen [F]all your promises are[Cadd9] gone, I'm the only o[G]ne...\n\n{c: Break}\n[F]  [G]  [F]  [G]  [F]  [G]  [F]  [G]\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[Am]Go on and hold her till the [D]screaming is [D]go[Dsus4]ne    [D]\n[Am]Go on believe her when she te[D]lls you nothing's [D]wr[Dsus4]ong   [D]\n[G]But, I'm the only one, who'll w[F]alk across the fire for y[Em]ou\n[G]And I'm the only one, who'll d[F]rown in my desire for y[Em]ou\n[Am]It's only fear that makes you run, the [Cadd9]demons that you're hiding from\nWhen [F]all your promises are [Cadd9]gone, I'm the only [G]one...  [F]     [Em]\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[G]And I'm the only one, who'll d[F]rown in my desire for y[Em]ou\n[Am]It's only fear that makes you run, the [Cadd9]demons that you're hiding from\nWhen [F]all your promises are [Cadd9]gone, I'm the only o[G]ne...\n\n{c: Outro}\n[G]I'm the only one...\n[G]I'm the only one...\n[G]Ain't nobody else is gonna love me...\n[G]Ain't nobody else is gonna love me...\n[G]\n","hash":"5f4733c165125a857949294d60693a85","key":10,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Im The Only One","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-07-30T20:44:36.326297Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"ec418bf5-62ad-4826-855d-da99e14a8f60","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Dur