nce with [E]me\nOw..\n\n{c: Solo}\n[E    |]       [E    |]       [E    |]       [B    |]\n\n{c: Bridge}\n[A]Said can I take you [B]home where [E]we can be a[A]lone\n\nNext we'll be movin' on\n\nHe was with me, yeah me\nN.C.\nAn' we'll be movin' on\n\nAn' singin' that same old song\n\nYeah with me, singin'\n\n{c: Chorus}\n(a cappella)\nN.C.\nI love rock n' roll\nN.C.\nSo put another dime in the jukebox, baby\nN.C.\nI love rock n' roll\nN.C.\nSo come an' take your time an' dance with me\n\n{c: Chorus}\n(x4)\n[E]I love rock n' roll\nSo [A]put another dime in the [B]jukebox, baby\n[E]I love rock n' roll\nSo [A]come an' take your time an' [B]dance with [E]me\n","hash":"3f837da12ad262ef1755ba76efd32204","key":7,"KeyShift":0,"name":"I Love Rock N Roll","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-09-11T03:02:05.897482Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"fc225600-9be1-4909-8194-27d98aaec12a","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"i love rock n roll\njoan jett and the blackhearts\ni saw him dancin' there by the record machine\ni love rock n' roll\nilrnr\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":219,"author":"Eric Church","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Verse 1}\n[G]Early Monday [Em]morning, 'til [C]Friday at [G]five\nMan I [G]work, work, [Em]work but I don't [C]climb, climb, [G]climb\nBoss [G]man can shove that [Em]overtime [C]up his [G]can\n[G]All I wanna [Em]do is put a [C]drink in my [G]hand\n\n{c: Chorus}\nYa [D]fill it up, I'll [C]throw it [G]down\nI got a [D]40 hour week worth of [C]trouble to [G]drown\nNo [G]need to compli[Em]cate it, I'm a [C]simple [G]man\n[G]All you gotta [Em]do is put a [C]drink in my [G]hand\n\n[G]  [G]  [G]  [G]  [G]  [G]  [G]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\nYeah, the [G]parking lot is [Em]muddy, can'