 in it for [Bb]life\nIf you're [Ab]not in it for [Bb]love\nLet me [F]make it [Ab]clear to you my dear  [Bb]\nN.C.\nYou're not in it for love, I'm outta here\n\n{c: Instrumental}\n|2 bar intro|C  x4|Bb x2|F  x2|C  x2|\n\n{c: Outro}\nIf you're [Ab]not [Eb]in it for [Bb]love\nIf you're [Ab]not [Eb]willin' to [Bb]give it all you got\nIf you're [Ab]not in it for [Bb]life\nIf you're [Ab]not in it for [Bb]love\nIf you're [Ab]not in it for [Bb]life\nIf you're [Ab]not in it for [Bb]love\nN.C.\nI'm outta here\n","hash":"88f8536d9de138be774dcf9253a9af7f","key":8,"KeyShift":0,"name":"If Youre Not In It For Love Im Outta Here","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-04-26T04:07:26.527506Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"1ead38f2-f3b2-4a0e-a53d-fe853b51d98e","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"if youre not in it for love im outta here\nshania twain\nmind if i sit down can i buy you a round\nif you're not in it for love\niyniiflioh\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":222,"author":"Tracy Byrd","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n{sot}\ne|---------------------------------------------------------------|\nB|---------------------------------------------------------------|\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------|\nD|-----3-------------5-----3-5-5-3---------5-----3-5-5-3---------|\nA|-3h5---5p3---3-------3h5---------5p3-------3h5---------5p3-----|\nE|-----------6---6-3-------------------6-3-------------------6-3-|\n{eot}\n\n{c: Verse 1}\nI was [G7]driving through Georgia in late July\non a day hot enough to make the [D]Devil [G7]sigh\nI saw a homemade sign [C]written in red\nRi[G7]nd County Watermelon [D]Festival [G7]ahead\n\n{c: Verse 2}\nWell I [G7]wasn't in a hurry so I slowed down\ntook a two lane road to a [D]one horse [G7]town\nthere was a party goin on when [C]I got there\n[G7]I heard a welcome speech from a [D]small town [G7]mayor\n\n{c: Chorus}\nHe said we [C]got 100 gallons of sweet red wine\n[G7]made from the biggest watermelons on the vine\nhelp you[C]rself to some but obey the law\nif you [G7]drink don't drive do the [D]Watermelon [G7]Crawl\n\n{c: Verse 3}\nWhen the [G7]band started playin a watermelon queen\nSaid let me show you something that you a[D]in't never [G7]seen\nshe grabbed me by the arm said c[C]'mon let's go\n[G7]she dipped down spun around and [D]do-si-[G7]do'd\n\n{c: Verse 4}\nShe [G]rocked back on her heels dropped down to her knees\ncrawled across the floor then she [D]jumped back to her [G7]feet\nshe wiggled and she jiggled - beat [C]all you ever saw\nsaid \"[G7]This is how you down the [D]Watermelon [G7]Crawl\n\n{c: Chorus}\nHe said we [C]got 100 gallons of sweet red wine\n[G7]made from the biggest watermelons on the vine\nhelp your[C]self to some but obey the law\nif you [G7]drink don't drive do the [D]Watermelon [G7]Crawl\n\n{c: Verse 5}\nIf you're [G]ever down in Georgia round about July\n\nif you ain't in a hurry then you oughta stop by\nI can guarantee you're [C]gonna have a ball\n[G]learnin' how to do the [D]Watermelon [G]Crawl\n\n{c: Chorus}\nHe said we [C]got 100 gallons of sweet red wine\n[G7]made from the biggest watermelons on the vine\nhelp your[C]self to some but obey the law\nif you [G]drink don't drive do the [D]Watermelon [G7]Crawl\nDo the w[G7]atermelon crawl  Have fun you all\n\nand do the watermelon craaaawwwwlllll\n","hash":"b211019b1cdc00f5fb59a980df59dfdf","key":10,"KeyShift":5,"name":"Watermelon Crawl","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-09-16T22:26:15.066173Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"9049b6aa-15bc-47c9-aa9d-e5dbb4755d9f","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"watermelon crawl\ntracy byr