as [C]come to leave you\n[G]One more time [C]let me kiss you\nThen [G]close your eyes [C]I'll be on my [D]way\n[G]Dream about the [C]days to come\nWhen [G]I won't have to [C]leave alone\nA[G]bout the times [C]I won't have to [D]say\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSo [G]kiss me and [C]smile for me\n[G]Tell me that you'll [C]wait for me\n[G]Hold me like you'll [C]never let me [D]go\nI'm [G]leaving [C]on a jet plane\n[G]   Don't know when [C]I'll be back again\n[G]  Oh babe, [C]I hate to [D]go\n\nI'm [G]leaving [C]on a jet plane\n[G]   Don't know when [C]I'll be back again\n[G]  Oh babe, [C]I hate to [D]go\n","hash":"b811b104ce4d8bae153ba961496d114d","key":10,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Leaving On A Jet Plane","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-11-27T02:47:40.370291Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"4b5bf263-55c8-4acb-ba68-7d808ddedbd1","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"leaving on a jet plane\njohn denver\nall my bags are packed i'm ready to go\nso kiss me and smile for me\nloajp\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":279,"author":"The Rolling Stones","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro/Verse}\n(lead guitar melody)\n{sot}\n   E       A         B       A\ne|-4-------5-4-5/7-|(7)------5-4-5-4-|\nB|-----------------|-----------------|\nG|-----------------|-----------------|\nD|-----------------|-----------------|\nA|-----------------|-----------------|\nE|-----------------|-----------------|\n{eot}\n\n/ = slide up into note, (7) = hold note over bar line\n\n{c: Intro}\n[E]    [A]    [B]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\nI [E]live on an a[A]partment on the [B]ninety ninth [A]floor of my bl[E]ock [A]    [B]    [A]\nAnd I [E]sit at home lookin' [A]out of the window i[B]maginin' the [A]world has stop[E]ped [A]    [B]    [A]\nThen [E]in flies a [A]guy who's all dressed [B]up just like a [A]Union Ja[E]ck  [A]    [B]    [A]\nAnd says [E]I've won five [A]pounds if I have [B]this kind of[A] detergent [E]pack [A]    [B]    [A]\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[D]Don't hang around, 'cause [B]two's a crowd on my cloud [E]baby [A]    [B]    [A]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\nThe [E]telephone is [A]ringin', I say [B]Hi it's me, who is it [A]there on the l[E]ine [A]    [B]    [A]\nA [E]voice says Hi hel[A]lo how are you, well [B]I guess I'm[A] doin' fi[E]ne  [A]    [B]    [A]\nHe says it's [E]three a.m., there's [A]too much noise, don't you [B]people ever wanna [A]go to be[E]d?  [A]    [B]    [A]\nJust cause [E]you feel so [A]good, do you have to [B]drive me [A]out of my he[E]ad  [A]    [B]    [A]\n\n{c: Chorus}\nI said [E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[D]Don't hang around, 'cause [B]two's a crowd on my cloud [E]baby [A]    [B]    [A]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\nI was [E]sick and tired, fed u[A]p with this and de[B]cided to take a [A]drive down to[E]wn  [A]    [B]    [A]\nIt was [E]so very quiet and [A]peaceful, there was [B]nobody, not a [A]soul arou[E]nd  [A]    [B]    [A]\nI [E]laid myself [A]out, I was so [B]tired and I [A]started to dr[E]eam [A]    [B]    [A]\nIn the [E]morning the parking [A]tickets were just like [B]flags, [A]stuck on my wind[E]screen [A]    [B]    [A]\n\n{c: Chorus}\nI said [E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[D]Don't hang around, 'cause [B]two's a crowd on my cloud\n\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[E]Hey (hey), [E/G#]you (you), get [A]off of my [B]cloud\n[D]Don't hang around, 'cause [B]two's a crowd on my cloud baby\n","hash":"490470b9a984fcb9972309a47d7dbbf3","key":7,"KeyShift":5,"name":"Get Off Of My Cloud","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-11-27T02:53:20.492400Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"c7223154-7484-4aae-ae29-af710b04d4a9","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"get off of my cloud\nthe rolling stones\ni live on an apartment on the ninety ninth floor of my block\nhey (hey) you (you) get off of my cloud\ngoomc\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":280,"author":"Eagles","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n[C]     [FM7   (x2)]\n\n{c: Verse}\n[C]Every night, I'm lying in bed, [FM7]holding you close in my dreams\n[C]Thinking about all the things that we said, and [FM7]coming apart at the seams\n[Em]We try to talk it o[Dm]ver, but the [Em]words come out too [F/G]rough\nI [C]know you were trying to [Dm]give me the best of your [C]love  [G7]\n\n{c: Verse}\n[C]Beautiful faces, and loud empty places,[FM7] look at the way that we live\n[C]Wasting our time on cheap talk and wine,[FM7] left us so little to give\nThat[Em] same old crowd was like a[Dm] cold dark cloud that[Em] we could never rise a[F/G]bove\nBut [C]here in my heart, I [Dm]give you the best of my [C]love  [G7]\n\n{c: Chorus}\nOh-oh-oh oh[C]hhh, sweet darlin',[Dm] you get the best of my love\nOh-oh-oh oh[Cmaj7/G]hhh, sweet darlin', you get the [Dm]best of my love\n\n{c: Bridge}\n[Fm7]I'm going back in time and it's a [C]sweet dream\nIt was a [Fm7]quiet night and I would be all right if I could [Dm]go on [G7]sleeping\n\n{c: Verse}\nBut [C]every morning I wake up and worry,[FM7] what's gonna happen today?\n[C]You see it your way, and I see it mine, but we [FM7]both see it slipping away\n[Em]You know we always had each [Dm]other baby,[Em] I guess that wasn't eno[Dm]ugh; [G7]o-o-ohh\nBut [C]here in my heart, I [Dm]give you the best of my [C]love  [G]\n\n{c: Chorus}\n(Repeat till fade)\nOh-oh-oh [C]ohhhh, sweet darlin',[Dm] you get the best of my love\nOh-oh-oh oh[Cmaj7/G]hhh, sweet darlin', you get the [Dm]best of my love\n","hash":"2c08d466b42ac7e7436c9976f2669b63","key":3,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Best Of My Love","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-11-27T03:13:46.905712Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"e5c094e8-a8a3-4c93-a0f8-251feef0e243","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"best of my love\neagles\nevery night i'm lying in bed holding you close in my dreams\noh-oh-oh ohhhh sweet darlin' you get the best of my love\nboml\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":281,"author":"Jay & The Americans","Capo":0,"content":"\n[C]   [Am]    [F]   [G]\n\n{c: Verse}\nThis magic [C]moment so [Am]different and so new\nWas like any [F]other until [G]I kissed you\nAnd then it [C]happened it [Am]took me by surprise\nI knew that you [F]felt it too by the [G]look in your eyes\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSweeter than [Am]wine (sweeter than wine)\nSofter than a [F]summer night\n                     (softer than a sumer night)\nEverything I [C]want I have whenever I [G]hold you tight\nThis magic [C]moment while your [Am]lips are close to mine\nWill last for[F]ever  for[G]ever till the end of [C]time\nwhoa  oh  oh  [Am]oh  oh  Whoa  oh  oh  [F]oh  oh    Whoa  oh  oh   [G]oh\n\nRepeat chorus, fade out with whoa o[C]h'[Am]sSu[F]bm[G]itted by Doug Morris, dougmorris@tce.snider.net\n","hash":"06c378f7bd8ca7058bf432cbd42c6754","key":3,"K