 out my [D7]window,\n[A7]what do you think I [D7]see?\n[A7]And when I look in my [D7]window,\n[A7]so many different p[D7]eople to be.\nIt's [A7]strange,[D7]\nsure is [A7]strange.[D7]\n\n[A7]You got to pick up every [D7]stitch,\n[A7]you got to pick up every [D7]stitch\n[A7]two rabbits running in the [D7]ditch.\n[A7]Oh no [D7]\n\n[D7]Must be the [E7]season of the [A]witch,\n[D7]must be the [E7]season of the [A]witch, yeah,\n[D7]must be the [E7]season of the [A7]witch.\n\n[A7]      [D7]    when I [A7]go   [D7]    When I [A7]go   [D7]     [A7]\n\nSet8\n","hash":"6ce82ec001b82bce619437ff3df6503b","key":5,"KeyShift":7,"name":"Season Of The Witch","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-12-04T02:50:22.434497Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"2094b005-faf2-4bde-bcc9-fa826d723a65","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"season of the witch\ndonovan\nwhen i look out my window\nsotw\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":287,"author":"Ben E. King","Capo":0,"content":"\n[C]\n\n#1.\n[C]Every time I kiss somebody new, I, uh, [E]make\nbelieve I'm kissing you but, uh, [Am7]I can't kid\nmy aching heart cause, uh, [F]my heart knows we're\nstill apart and, [Dm]uh..\n\n{c: CHORUS}\n[C]Each night is like a thousand [Am7]years, oh, [C]oh..\n[F]I can't [G]lose these young boy [C]blues.\n\n#2.\n[C]I wanna cry when I hear your name, but, [E]if I cry,\nI feel ashamed, so..[Am7]I let my pride be my guide,\n[G]then, [F]I keep those tears inside, [Am7]so..\n\n{c: CHORUS}\n[C]Each night is like a thousand [Am7]years, oh, [C]oh..\n[F]Since I [G]got these young boy [C]blues..[C7]mmmmmmmm..mmmmm..\n\n{c: BRIDGE}\n[F]Don't know where to go..don't know what to do.\n[C]I'm so lonesome and [Am7]lonely, [Dm]since I [Am]lost[Gb]....[G]you[G7].\n\n#3.\n[C]Every time I kiss somebody new, I, uh, [E]make\nbelieve I'm kissing you but, uh, [Am7]I can't kid\nmy aching heart cause, uh, [F]my heart knows we're\n\nstill apart and uh..\n\n{c: CHORUS}\n[C]Each night is like a thousand [Am7]years, [E]oh, [Am7]oh.. [G]\n[F]I can't [G]lose these young boy [C]blues..[Am7]mmmmm..[C]mmmm..\n\nOUTRO:\n[C]Each night is like a thousand [Am7]years, [E]oh, [Am7]oh.. [C]\n[F]I can't [G]lose these young boy [C]blues.[Am7]....[C]..(Fade.)\n\nA sixties smash from Kraziekhat.\n","hash":"796070c2c51a67e74bbd1f5a9cdcbd8b","key":3,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Young Boy Blues","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-12-04T03:06:49.424198Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"bae72598-1e69-437f-aa4f-20583bd42351","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"young boy blues\nben e king\n#1\neach night is like a thousand years oh oh\nybb\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":288,"author":"Atlanta Rhythm Section","Capo":0,"content":"\n[A13]Bbm6    6x868x (or is it Bbdim ?)\n\n\nThese 4 chords are movable, just go up 1 fret on the neck when the song goes up 1/2 step after Verse 2.\n\n{c: Intro}\n[Bm7]    [Bm7]    [Bm7]    [Bm7]\n[Em7]    [A13]    [Em7]    [A13]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\n[Em7]In the cool of the evenin' when [A13]ev'rything is gettin' kind of [Em7]groovy    [A13]\n[Em7]I call you up and ask you if you'd [A13]like to go with me and see a [Em7]movie     [A13]\n[Em7]First you say \"No\", you've got some plans for the night\nAnd then you [A13]stop, and say, [Bbm6]\"All right\"\n[Em7]Love is kinda crazy with a [A13]spooky little girl like [Em7]you.  [Bm7]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\n[Em7]You always keep me guessin', I [A13]never seem to know what you are [Em7]thinkin'  [A13]\n[Em7]And if some fellow looks at you, it's for [A13]sure your little eye will be a-[Em7]winkin'   [A13]\n[Em7]I get confused, 'cause I don't know where I stand\nAnd then you [A13]smile, and [Bbm6]hold my hand\n[Em7]Love is kinda crazy with a [A13]spooky little girl like [Em7]you … [Bm7]Spooky! [Cm7]Spooky! Yeah - yeah\n\n{c: Guitar Solo}\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]\n[Bb13]     [Bm6]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Cm7]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[Fm7]If you decide someday to [Bb13]stop this little game that you are [Fm7]playin'    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]I'm gonna tell you all that my [Bb13]heart's been a-dyin' to be [Fm7]sayin'    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]Just like a ghost, you've been a-hauntin' my dreams\nSo I'll pro[Bb13]pose... on [Bm6]Halloween.\n[Fm7]Baby, love is kinda crazy with a [Bb13]spooky little girl like [Fm7]you … Ah, [Cm7]spooky, yeah-uh!\n\n{c: Guitar Solo}\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]\n[Bb13]     [Bm6]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Cm7]\n\n{c: Piano Solo}\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]\n[Bb13]     [Bm6]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Cm7]\n\n{c: Guitar Solo}\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]    [Bb13]\n[Fm7]\n[Bb13]     [Bm6]\n[Fm7]    [Bb13]     [Fm7]\n\n{c: Ending}\n[Cm7]    [Cm7]    [Cm7]    [Cm7]\n","hash":"d1654d2c2efb167802263dc3e28c42e0","key":6,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Spooky","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2024-12-04T04:01:24.032906Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"a89607f6-5b56-49c4-8ff3-fa730bbac181","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"spooky\natlanta rhythm section\nin the cool of the evenin' when ev'rything is gettin' kind of groovy\ns\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChi