id you fo[F#m]rget about me, Mr. Du[F#m]plicity?\nI hate to [B]bug you in the middle of d[B]inner.\nIt was a [F#m]slap in the face how quickly [F#m]I was replaced,\nand are you t[B]hinking of me when you [B]fuck her?\n\n{c: Pre-Chorus}\n'Cause the [F#m]love that you gave that we made\nwasn't able to[A] make it enough for you to be[B] open wide. No[B],\n[F#m]and every time you speak her name\ndoes she [A]know how you told me you'd hold me\nunt[B]il you died? Till you died, but you're [B]still alive.\n\n{c: Chorus}\nAnd I'm [F#]here to remind[E] you\nof the mess[A] you left when you went[B] away.\nIt's not [F#]fair to de[E]ny me\nof the cr[A]oss I bear that you [B]gave to me.\n[B]You, you, you oughta know.\n\n{c: Interlude}\n[F#m]\n\n{c: Bridge}\nCause the [F#m]joke that you laid in the bed that was me,\nand I'm n[A]ot gonna fade as soon as you[B] close your eyes, and you kno[B]w it.\nAnd [F#m]every time I scratch my nails down\n[A]someone else's back\nI hope you [B]feel it. Can you feel it?[B]\n\n{c: Chorus}\nAnd I'm [F#]here to remind[E] you\nof the mess[A] you left when you went[B] away.\nIt's not [F#]fair to de[E]ny me\nof the cr[A]oss I bear that you [B]gave to me.\n[B]You, you, you oughta know.\n","hash":"650907eac7e9cc997de34e028d42a1c0","key":7,"KeyShift":0,"name":"You Oughta Know","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-26T03:00:57.011263Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"85a468ed-efa4-41d5-8f72-64838356c4bf","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"you oughta know\nalanis morissette\ni want you to know that i'm happy for you\nand i'm here to remind you\nyok\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":320,"author":"ZZ Top","Capo":0,"content":"{sot}\n   G C/G   C F/C\ne|-3--3--|-x--x--|\