[D]soul [A]deep.\n[A]Way down inside me it's [D]soul [A]deep.\nMy [A]love is a river running [D]soul [A]deep.\n[A]Way down inside me it's [D]soul [A]deep.\nMy [A]love is a river running [D]soul [A]deep.\n[A]Way down inside me it's [D]soul [A]deep.\n\n(fade out)\n\nA sixties smash from Kraziekhat.\n","hash":"89f26cec9a99e41519d56e95dcf4e288","key":0,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Soul Deep","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-20T00:25:54.059059Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"c01ed29f-2b45-41d3-ad21-3b62752b3fb9","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"soul deep\nthe box tops\ndarlin' i don't know much\nand my love is a river running soul deep\nsd\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":323,"author":"America","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n(tab relative to capo)\n{sot}\n   Am      F       C   Csus4 C          Em\ne|-------------------------------------7~--------|\nB|----------------------------------8------------|\nG|------------------------------7/9--------------|\nD|-----------------------------------------------|\nA|-----------------------------------------------|\nE|-----------------------------------------------|\n{eot}\n\n{sot}\n  (Em)        Am          G           F\ne|-----------8~------8\\7-7~------7\\5-5~----------|\nB|--------8--------------------------------------|\nG|----7/9----------------------------------------|\nD|-----------------------------------------------|\nA|-----------------------------------------------|\nE|-----------------------------------------------|\n{eot}\n\n{c: Verse 1}\nWell, I tr[C]ied to make it Sunday, but I [Em]got so damn depressed,\nthat I s[F]et my sights on M[C]onday and I g[Em]ot myself undressed\nI ain't r[F]eady for the al[Dm]tar, but I [Am]do a[Em]gree there's ti[F]mes,\nwhen a w[Dm]oman sure can [F]be a friend of [C]mine[Csus4]      [C]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\nWell, I k[C]eep on thinkin' 'bout you, Sister G[Em]olden Hair surprise,\nand I j[F]ust can't live witho[C]ut you; can't you s[Em]ee it in my eyes?\nI been o[F]ne poor corresp[Dm]ondent, and I been t[Am]oo, too [Em]hard to fi[F]nd,\nbut it d[Dm]oesn't mean you a[F]in't been on my m[C]ind\n\n{c: Chorus}\nWill you m[G]eet me in the middle, will you m[F]eet me in the a[C]ir?\nWill you lo[G]ve me just a little, just en[F]ough to show you c[C]are?\nWell I t[Dm]ried to fake it, I d[Em]on't mind sayin', I j[F]ust can't make it\n\n{c: Instrumental}\n[Am]      [F]     [C]    [Csus4]      [C]\n[Em](Repeat int[Am]ro rif[G]f)   [F]\n\n{c: Verse 4}\nWell, I k[C]eep on thinkin' 'bout you, Sister G[Em]olden Hair surprise,\nand I j[F]ust can't live with[C]out you; can't you s[Em]ee it in my eyes?\nI been o[F]ne poor corresp[Dm]ondent, and I been [Am]too, too h[Em]ard to f[F]ind,\nbut it d[Dm]oesn't mean you a[F]in't been on my m[C]ind\n\n{c: Chorus}\nWill you m[G]eet me in the middle, will you m[F]eet me in the a[C]ir?\nWill you l[G]ove me just a little, just en[F]ough to show you c[C]are?\nWell I t[Dm]ried to fake it, I d[Em]on't mind sayin', I j[F]ust can't make it\n\n{c: Outro}\nD[G]oo wop shoo wop, Doo wop shoo wop, D[F]oo wop shoo wop, D[C]oo wop shoo wop\nD[G]oo wop shoo wop, Doo wop shoo wop, D[F]oo wop shoo wop, D[C]oo wop shoo wop\nD[G]oo wop shoo wop, Doo wop shoo wop, D[F]oo wop shoo wop, D[C]oo wop shoo wop\nD[G]oo wop shoo wop, Doo wop shoo wop, D[F]oo wop shoo wop, D[C]oo wop shoo wop\n","hash":"f1227b073f48a8bc6849ea90c7d6bafc","key":3,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Sister Golden Hair","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-20T00:27:31.523410Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"f1e6affe-1ae6-449d-89ed-9d966dcef4a1","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"sister golden hair\name