me,[Fm]....\ns[Am7]ince I..f[G]ell...for[Cmaj7] you ..[F]..[C]..[C7].\n\n{c: Chorus}\n* Well it's [F]too bad, and it's[Fm] too sad,\nBut [Cmaj7]I'm still  in l[Dmin7]ove with you  [C]   [C7]\nFirst you lo[F]ve me, then you s[Fm]nub me.\nBut [Cmaj7]what can I d[Am7]o   'cause  I[Fm7]'m still in lo[G]ve with you.\n\nWell [Cmaj7]I.....[Am7]......gu[F]ess I'll never s[G]ee the\n[Cmaj7]light...[Am7]....[F]I get the blu[G]es most ev-ery [F]nigh[Fm]t,.....\ns[Am7]ince I f[G]ell.....for y[C]ou .[F].. [C]    [C7]       [F]   [Fm]\n.......S[Am7]ince I f[G]ell.. for---  [Cmaj7]you....\n","hash":"20e916fef11e0d244b81b7476926f3cf","key":3,"KeyShift":7,"name":"Since I Fell For You","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-20T01:25:26.060524Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"06a7df64-7660-464e-a943-a38556070017","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"since i fell for you\nlenny welch\nyoumade me leave my happy home\n* well it's too bad and it's too sad\nsiffy\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":327,"author":"Johnny Rivers","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n{sot}\ne|-0-0-0-----------0-0-0----------0-0-0------------------|\nB|-5-3-0-0---0-----5-3-0-0---0----5-3-0-0---0------------|\nG|-------0h2-0-----------0h2-0----------0h2-0------------|\nD|-------------2---------------2--------------2--2-2-----|\nA|-----------------------------------------------2-2-----|\nE|-----------------------------------------------0-0-----|\n{eot}\n\n[E]\n\nLong [B7]distance information, give me Memphis Tennessee\n\nHelp me find a party that tried to get in touch with me\nShe [E]could not leave a number but I [E7]know who placed the [E]call\n'Cause my [B7]uncle took a message and he wrote it on the [E]wall\n\n[B7]Help me, information, get in touch with my Marie\n\nShe's the only one who'd call me here from Memphis Tennessee\nHer [E]home is on the south side, [E7]high upon a [E]ridge\n[B7]Just a half a mile from the [B]Mississippi [E]bridge\n\n[B7]     [E]  [E7]   [E]    [B7]   [B]  [E]\n\nLast [B7]time I saw Marie she was wavin' me goodbye\n\nWith \"hurry-home\" drops on her cheek that trickled from her eye\nBut [E]we were pulled apart because her [E7]mom did not a[E]gree\nAnd [B7]tore apart our happy home in [B]Memphis Tennes[E]see\n\n[B7]Help me, information, more than that I cannot add\n\nOnly that I miss her and all the fun we had\nMa[E]rie is only six years old, [E7]information [E]please\n[B7]Try to put me through to her in [B]Memphis Tennes[E]see\n\n[E]   [B7]    [B]   [E]\n\n* Alternate:\n\nCapo II\n\n[A7]\n[D]\n[D7]\n[A]\n\nSet8\n","hash":"0e021a359bfdcb1cc131b7006d8f04df","key":7,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Memphis","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-20T01:37:04.851335Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"6a7ae244-deae-43b0-8cf5-54e57de878c9","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"memphis\njohnny rivers\ne|-0-0-0-----------0-0-0----------0-0-0------------------|\nm\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":328,"author":"Johnny Rivers","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n[Em]   [E]   [C]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\n[Em]There's a man who [Am]leads a life of [Em]danger\nTo [Em]everyone he meets he stays a [B7]stranger\nWith [Em]every move he makes, a[Am]nother chance he takes\n[Em]Odds are he won't [Am]live to see to[Em]morrow\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSecret [Bm]agent [Em]man, secret [Bm]agent [Em]man\nThey've [C]given you a [B7]number and taken away your [Em]name [Em]   [E]   [C]  [Em]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\nBe[Em]ware of pretty [Am]faces that you [Em]find\nA [Em]pretty face can hide an evil [B7]mind\nAh, be [Em]careful what you say, Or [Am]you'll give yourself away\n[Em]Odds are you won't [Am]live to see to[Em]morrow\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSecret [Bm]agent [Em]man, secret [Bm]agent [Em]man\nThey've [C]given you a [B7]number and taken away your [Em]name [Em]   [E]   [C]  [Em]\n\n{c: Instrumental}\n[Em]    [Am]    [Em]     [Em]     [B7]     [Em]     [Am]     [Em]     [Am]     [Em]\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSecret [Bm]agent [Em]man, secret [Bm]agent [Em]man\nThey've [C]given you a [B7]number and taken away your [Em]name [Em]   [E]   [C]  [Em]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[Em]Swingin' on the [Am]Riviera [Em]one day\nAnd then [Em]layin' in the Bombay alley [B7]next day\nOh [Em]no, you let the wrong word slip, [Am]while kissing persuasive lips\nThe [Em]odds are you won't [Am]live to see to[Em]morrow\n\n{c: Chorus}\nSecret [Bm]agent [Em]man, secret [Bm]agent [Em]man\nThey've [C]given you a [B7]number and taken away your [Em]name\n\n{c: Outro}\n[Em]   [E]   [C]\n\nSet8\n","hash":"d8af8f051b4894063e5f2147a5df4f02","key":10,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Secret Agent Man","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-03-20T01:40:37.450076Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"4ead3b7f-0d4f-4dc5-865a-7e0c6f02565a","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"secret agent man\njohnny rivers\nthere's a man who leads a life of danger\nsecret agent man secret agent man\nsam\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":329,"author":"Johnny Rivers","Capo":0,"content":"\n[D]Do-doo-doo-wah shoo-be-[Em]doo-be [D]  [Em]\n[D]Do-doo-doo-wah shoo-be-[Em]doo-be [D]  [Em]\n\n[D]How can you tell me how much you [Em]miss me?\n[D]When the last time I saw you, you wouldn't even [Em]kiss me\nThat [G]rich guy you