ck\nCarry me back, baby, where I come [A]from, whoa-oh, oh\nIt’s [E]been a long time, been a long time\nBeen a long [D]lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely [A]time\n\n{c: Interlude}\n[A  |]      [A   |]      [A   |]      [A   |]\n[A   |]      [A   |]      [A   |]      [A   |]\n[D   |]      [D   |]      [A   |]      [A   |]\n[E   |]      [E   |]      [A   |]      [A   |]\n\n{c: Solo}\n[A   |]      [A   |]      [A     |]        [A    |]\n[A   |]      [A   |]      [A     |]        [A    |]\n[D   |]      [D   |]      [D     |]        [D    |]\n[A   |]      [A   |]      [A     |]        [A    |]\n[E   |]      [E   |]      [D|]\n  [A]      [A]      [A]        [A]Ohhhh\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[A]Seems so long since we walked in the moonlight\n\nMaking vows that just can’t work right\nOh yeah, [D]open your arms, open your arms\nOpen your arms, baby, let my love come [A]running in\nIt’s [E]been a long time, been a long time\nBeen a long [D]lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely [A]time\n\n{c: Outro}\n[A]  Yeah-hey, yeah-hey\n[A]  Yeah-hey, yeah-hey\n[D]\n\n[A]  Ooh yeah… ooh yeah\n\nOoh yeah… ooh yeah\nIt’s [E]been a long time, been a long time\nBeen a long [D]lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely, lonely time\n\n{c: Ending}\n(Drum fill)\n[A7]\n","hash":"904a8b388f78a855aa2081994feba947","key":0,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Rock And Roll","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-05-13T23:00:48.287322Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"1639ea6f-243c-472f-b980-9514df0dbcc3","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"rock and roll\nled zeppelin\nit’s been a long time since i rock and rolled\nrar\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":354,"author":"Adele","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Intro}\n[Am]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\n[Am]There's a fire 