olders\": \"[]\",\n      \"drawingPathsBackup\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"Id\": 191,\n      \"author\": \"Tom Petty and The Heartbreakers\",\n      \"Capo\": 0,\n      \"content\": \"{c: Intro}\\n[Am]     [G]    [Dsus2]        [Am   (x4)]\\n\\n{c: Verse}\\n[Am]She grew up in an [G]Indiana town\\nHad a [Dsus2]good-lookin' mama who [Am]never was around\\nBut she [Am]grew up tall and she [G]grew up right\\nWith them [Dsus2]Indiana boys on an [Am]Indiana night\\n\\n[Am]     [G]    [Dsus2]        [Am   (x2)]\\n\\n{c: Verse 2}\\nWell, she [Am]moved down here at the [G]age of eighteen\\nShe [Dsus2]blew the boys away, was [Am]more than they'd seen\\n[Am]I was introduced and we [G]both started groovin'\\nShe [Dsus2]said, \\\"I dig you baby but I [Am]got to keep movin'\\\"\\n\\n[Am]...on[G],   [Dsus2]  keep movin' on[Am]\\n[Am]     [G]    [Dsus2]        [Am]\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\n[Em7]Last dance with Mary Jane\\n[Em7]One more time to kill the pa[A]in\\n[Em7]I feel summer creepin' in and I'm\\n[Em7]Tired of this town aga[A]in   [G]\\n\\n[Am]     [G]    [Dsus2]        [Am   (x2)]\\n\\n{c: Verse 3}\\nWell, [Am]I don't know, but [G]I've been told\\nYou [Dsus2]never slow down, you [Am]never grow old\\nI'm [Am]tired of screwing up, I'm [G]tired of going down\\n[Dsus2]Tired of myself, [Am]tired of this town\\n\\n[Am]Oh my my, [G]oh hell yes\\n[Dsus2]Honey, put on that [Am]party dress\\n[Am]Buy me a drink, [G]sing me a song,\\n[Dsus2]Take me as I come 'cause I [Am]can't stay long\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\n[Em7]Last dance with Mary Jane\\n[Em7]One more time to kill the pa[A]in\\n[Em7]I feel summer creepin' in and I'm\\n[Em7]Tired of this town ag[A]ain   [G]\\n\\n{c: Solo}\\n[Am]     [G]    [Dsus2]        [Am   (x4)]\\n\\n{c: Verse 4}\\nThere's [Am]pigeons down on [G]Market Square\\n[Dsus2]She's standin' in her [Am]underwear\\n[Am]Lookin' down from a [G]hotel room\\n[Dsus2]Nightfall will be [Am]comin' soon\\n\\n[Am]Oh my my, [G]oh hell yes\\nYou [Dsus2]got to put on that [Am]party dress\\nIt was [Am]too cold to cry when I [G]woke up alone\\nI [Dsus2]hit my last number and [Am]walked to the road\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\n[Em7]Last dance with Mary Jane\\n[Em7]One more time to kill the pa[A]in\\n[Em7]I feel summer creepin' in and I'm\\n[Em7]Tired of this town ag[A]ain   [G]\\n\\n[Am](Play[G] ove[Dsus2]r and ov[Am]er till out, with solo guitar and harmonica)\\n\",\n      \"hash\": \"296d6d03cdef9472af5f85af97f5c83b\",\n      \"key\": 10,\n      \"KeyShift\": 0,\n      \"name\": \"Mary Janes Last Dance\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"\",\n      \"type\": 1,\n      \"ModifiedDateTime\": \"2025-07-13T19:05:02.114284Z\",\n      \"Deleted\": false,\n      \"SyncId\": \"54f9b720-4197-4d0f-a6fe-3ba57a3ca257\",\n      \"timeSig\": \"\",\n      \"ZoomFactor\": 1.0,\n      \"Duration\": 0,\n      \"Duration2\": 0,\n      \"_displayParams\": \"{}\",\n      \"TempoInt\": 0,\n      \"_tags\": \"[]\",\n      \"Url\": \"\",\n      \"DeepSearch\": \"mary janes last dance\\ntom petty and the heartbreakers\\nshe grew up in an indiana town\\nlast dance with mary jane\\nmjld\\n\",\n      \"Copyright\": \"\",\n      \"NotesText\": \"\",\n      \"Zoom\": 1.0,\n      \"SectionOrder\": \"\",\n      \"SongNumber\": 0,\n      \"HasChildren\": 0,\n      \"ParentId\": 0,\n      \"vName\": null,\n      \"locked\": 0,\n      \"LinkedAudio\": null,\n      \"Chords\": null,\n      \"midiOnLoad\": null,\n      \"_folders\": \"[]\",\n      \"drawingPathsBackup\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"Id\": 319,\n      \"author\": \"The Beatles\",\n      \"Capo\": 0,\n      \"content\": \"\\nYou [A]say you want a revolution, well you [D]know\\nWe all want to change the [A]world\\nYou tell me that it's evolution, well you [D]know\\nWe all want to change the [E7]wor[E]ld\\n\\n[Bm] but when you talk about de[E]struction\\n[Bm] don't you know that you can [G]count [A]me [F#]out  [E]\\n\\nDon't you know it's gonna [A]be, al[D]right 3x\\n\\n[E]  [E7]    [E]  [E7]\\n\\nYou [A]say you got a real solution, well you [D]know\\nWe'd all love to see the [A]plan\\nYou ask me for a contribution, well you [D]know\\nWe're all doing what we [E7]can[E]\\n\\n[Bm] But if you want money for people with [E]minds that hate\\n[Bm] All I can tell you is brother you [G]have [A]to [F#]wait [E]\\n\\nDon't you know it's gonna [A]be, al[D]right 3x\\n\\n[E]  [E7]    [E]  [E7]\\n\\nYou [A]say you'll change the constitution, well you [D]know\\nWe all want to change your [A]head\\nYou tell me it's the institution, well you [D]know\\nYou better free your mind in[E7]ste[E]ad\\n\\n[Bm] But if you go carrying pictures of [E]Chairman Mao\\n[Bm] You ain't gonna make it with anyone [G]any[A]  h[F#]ow  [E]\\n\\nDon't you know it's gonna [A]be, al[D]right 3x\\nAl[A]right\\n\\n* Alternate:\\n\\nCapo II\\n\\n[G]\\n[C]\\n[D]\\n[D7]\\n[Am]\\n[F]\\n[E]\\n\\n** Revolution 2 version:\\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K725OnVB4dw\\n\\n*** It has been suggested that instead of Bm, Bm/F# be substituted\\n\\nSet8\\n\",\n      \"hash\": \"67536fd650b16c503a1b059a8be759b8\",\n      \"key\": 0,\n      \"KeyShift\": 2,\n      \"name\": \"Revolution\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"\",\n      \"type\": 1,\n      \"ModifiedDateTime\": \"2025-07-27T18:54:46.967537Z\",\n      \"Deleted\": false,\n      \"SyncId\": \"678c99f9-f81f-4a36-b986-7c2b5f391664\",\n      \"timeSig\": \"\",\n      \"ZoomFactor\": 1.0,\n      \"Duration\": 0,\n      \"Duration2\": 0,\n      \"_displayParams\": \"{}\",\n      \"TempoInt\": 0,\n      \"_tags\": \"[]\",\n      \"Url\": \"\",\n      \"DeepSearch\": \"revolution\\nthe beatles\\nyou say you want a revolution well you know\\nr\\n\",\n      \"Copyright\": \"\",\n      \"NotesText\": \"\",\n      \"Zoom\": 0.8085297624600705,\n      \"SectionOrder\": \"\",\n      \"SongNumber\": 0,\n      \"HasChildren\": 0,\n      \"ParentId\": 0,\n      \"vName\": null,\n      \"locked\": 0,\n      \"LinkedAudio\": null,\n      \"Chords\": null,\n      \"midiOnLoad\": null,\n      \"_folders\": \"[]\",\n      \"drawingPathsBackup\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"Id\": 122,\n      \"author\": \"The Doobie Brothers\",\n      \"Capo\": 0,\n      \"content\": \"{c: Verse}\\n[Gm7]Down around the corner, half a mile from here\\nSee them long trains run, and you watch them disappear\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\nWithout [Cm7]love, where would you be[Gm7] now\\nWithout [Eb]lo-[Dsus4]-o----[D]o-[Gm7]ove\\n\\n{c: Verse}\\nYou [Gm7]know I saw miss Lucy down along the tracks\\nShe lost her home and her family and she won't be coming back\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\nWithout [Cm7]love, where would you be ri\\nght [Gm7]now\\n\\nWithout [Eb]lo-[Dsus4]-o----[D]o-[Gm7]ove\\n\\n{c: Verse}\\nWell the [Gm7]Illinois Central\\nAnd the [Gm7]Southern Central Freight\\nGot to [Gm7]keep on pushin' mama\\nYou [Gm7]know they're running late\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\nWithout [Cm7]love, where would you be now\\n\\nWithout [Eb]lo-[Dsus4]-o----[D]o-[Gm7]ove\\n\\n[Gm7]       [Cm7]    [Gm7]\\n[Eb]   [Dsus4]      [D]  [Gm7]\\n\\n{c: Verse}\\n[Gm7]Well the Illinois Central\\nAnd the [Gm7]Southern Central Freight\\nGot to [Gm7]keep on pushin' mama\\nYou [Gm7]know they're running late\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\nWithout [Cm7]love, where would you be now\\n\\nWithout [Eb]lo-[Dsus4]-o----[D]o-[Gm7]ove\\n\\n{c: Verse}\\nWell the [Gm7]pistons keep on turning\\n[F]And the [Gm7]wheels go round and round [F]\\nThe [Gm7]steel rails are cold and hard\\n[F]For the [Gm7]miles that they go down\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\n[Cm7]Without love, where would you be right now\\nWithout [Eb]lo-[Dsus4]o------[D]ove\\n\\n[Cm7]ooh\\nWhere would you be now\\n\",\n      \"hash\": \"839343a67d79335f51dfc0f899b5ae23\",\n      \"key\": 1,\n      \"KeyShift\": 0,\n      \"name\": \"Long Train Runnin\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"\",\n      \"type\": 1,\n      \"ModifiedDateTime\": \"2025-07-20T19:45:03.038698Z\",\n      \"Deleted\": false,\n      \"SyncId\": \"9dbcd490-a8f4-4a07-b9c7-a8c691a3ccd4\",\n      \"timeSig\": \"\",\n      \"ZoomFactor\": 1.0,\n      \"Duration\": 0,\n      \"Duration2\": 235,