ned so s[Bb]oon.\\n[A]What could you d[Dm]ooooooooooo?\\n\\n{c: Solo}\\n[Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]\\n[Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]  [Dm]    [|]\\n\\n{c: Chorus}\\n[Gm]Black velvet in that li[C]ttle boy's smile.\\n[Gm]Black velvet in with that s[Eb]low s[Bb]outhern style.\\n[Gm]A new religion that'll b[C]ring you to your knees,\\n[Bb]Black ve[A]lvet, if you pl[Dm]ease.\\n\",\n      \"hash\": \"62e773f1fc94156c3404a2f5e091bfe1\",\n      \"key\": 20,\n      \"KeyShift\": 2,\n      \"name\": \"Black Velvet\",\n      \"subTitle\": \"\",\n      \"type\": 1,\n      \"ModifiedDateTime\": \"2024-08-10T00:10:39.296958Z\",\n      \"Deleted\": false,\n      \"SyncId\": \"86fe8687-ae3b-4f03-8213-ccba70aaa233\",\n      \"timeSig\": \"\",\n      \"ZoomFactor\": 1.0,\n      \"Duration\": 0,\n      \"Duration2\": 0,\n      \"_displayParams\": \"{}\",\n      \"TempoInt\": 0,\n      \"_tags\": \"[]\",\n      \"Url\": \"\",\n      \"DeepSearch\": \"black velvet\\nalannah myles\\nmississippi in the middle of a dry spell\\nblack velvet in that little boy's smile\\nbv\\n\",\n      \"Copyright\": \"\",\n      \"NotesText\": \"\",\n      \"Zoom\": 1.0,\n      \"SectionOrder\": \"\",\n      \"SongNumber\": 0,\n      \"HasChildren\": 0,\n      \"ParentId\": 0,\n      \"vName\": null,\n      \"locked\": 0,\n      \"LinkedAudio\": null,\n      \"Chords\": null,\n      \"midiOnLoad\": null,\n      \"_folders\": \"[]\",\n      \"drawingPathsBackup\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"Id\": 85,\n      \"author\": \"David Bowie\",\n      \"Capo\": 0,\n      \"content\": \"{c: Verse}\\n[A]Hey Man             [F]Leave me a-lone you [G]know\\n[A]Hey Man  Oh Henry  G[F]et off the p[G]hone I gotta\\n[A]Hey Man, I gotta\\n[B]Straighten my face This [D]mellow thighed chick just put my\\n[F]Spine out of [G]place\\n\\n[A]Hey Man, my sch[F]ool days insane     [G]\\n[A]Hey Man, my w[F]orks down the dr[G]ain\\n[A]Hey Man, Well She's a T[B]otal Blam Blam,\\n[D]She said she had to sque