ain,\n[E]Destination [A]Bangor, Maine.\n[A]Old worn out [D]suit and shoes,\n[E]I don't pay no union dues.\n\nI smoke...[A]old stogies [D]I have found,\n[E]Short, but not [A]too big around.\n[A]I'm a man of [D]means by no means,\n[E]King of the [A]road.\n\n(Key change from [A] to [A#])\n\n{c: Bridge}\nI know...[A#]every engineer on [D#]every train,\n[F]All their children, 'n all [A#]of their names,\nAnd...[A#]every handout in [D#]every town,\nAnd...[F]every lock that ain't locked when no one's around.\n\n{c: Verse 3}\nI sing...[A#]trailers for [D#]sale or rent,\n[F]Rooms to let, [A#]fifty cents,\n[A#]No phone, no [D#]pool, no pets.\n[F]I ain't got no cigarettes.\n\nAh, but...[A#]two hours of [D#]pushin' broom,\nBuys an [F]eight by twelve [A#]four-bit room.\nI'm a...[A#]man of [D#]means by no means,\n[F]King of the [A#]road.\n\n{c: Outro}\n(bass only)\n[A#]Trailers for [D#]sale or rent,\n[F]Rooms to let, [A#]fifty cents,\n[A#]No phone, no [D#]pool, no pets.\n[F]I ain't got no cigarettes.\nAh, but, [A#]two hours of [D#]pushin' broom,\nBuys an [F]eight by twelve [A#]four-bit room...\n","hash":"eed0f5084d8471ae24e4bf21ca1a6b7e","key":0,"KeyShift":0,"name":"King Of The Road","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-08-26T21:55:03.018660Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"3b63e3ca-f8a7-40d3-99ab-42c0f0c92a08","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"king of the road\nroger miller\ntrailers for sale or rent\nkotr\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":400,"author":"Stevie Ray Vaughan & Double Trouble","Capo":0,"content":"{c: Verse}\n[Am]Once was a sweet thing, baby\n[Am]Held that love in our hands\n[Am]But now I reach to kiss your lips\n[Am]It just don't mean a thing\n\n{c: Chorus}\n[Dm]And that's a c