]Got my mojo working\nGot my [A]mojo working\nGot my [E]mojo working\nGot my [B7]mojo working, but it [A]just won't work on [E]you    [B7]\n\n{c: Instrumental}\n[E]  [A]  [E]   [B]   [A]   [E]   [B7]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[B7]I got a gy[E]psy woman givin' me advice\nI got a [A]gypsy woman givin' me ad[E]vice\nI got a [B]whole lot of tricks [A]keeping here on [E]ice    [B7]\n\n{c: Outro}\n[E]\n","hash":"3003bddf2b9b64019ebe4f486106bbba","key":7,"KeyShift":0,"name":"Got My Mojo Working","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-08-26T15:58:50.200272Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"c94faab6-21e0-4993-a6b1-1a5d2ec31b9a","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"got my mojo working\nmuddy waters\ngot my mojo working but it just won't work on you\ngmmw\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":402,"author":"Melanie","Capo":0,"content":"\n{c: Introduction}\n[E]  [A]  [E]   [B]   [A]   [E]   [B7]\n\n{c: Verse 1}\nGot my [E]mojo working, but it just won't work on you\nGot my [A]mojo working, but it just won't work on [E]you\nI wanna [B7]love you so bad  [A]I don't know what to [E]do      [B7]\n\n{c: Verse 2}\n[B7]I'm going [E]down to Louisiana to get me a mojo hand\n[E]I'm going [A]down to Louisiana to get me a mojo [E]hand\n[E]I'm gonna [B7]have all you women [A]fetchin' at my com[E]mand      [B7]\n\n{c: Bridge}\nGot my [E]mojo working\n[E]Got my mojo working\nGot my [A]mojo working\nGot my [E]mojo working\nGot my [B7]mojo working, but it [A]just won't work on [E]you    [B7]\n\n{c: Instrumental}\n[E]  [A]  [E]   [B]   [A]   [E]   [B7]\n\n{c: Verse 3}\n[B7]I got a gy[E]psy woman givin' me advice\nI got a [A]gypsy woman givin' me ad[E]vice\nI got a [B]whole lot of tricks [A]keeping here on [E]ice    [B7]\n\n{c