]n\nDamn your ey[Bm7]es\n\n[E9]   [Bm7]    [E9]\n\n[Gmaj7]You keep deliberately de[F#7]ceiving me\n[Gmaj7]Making me see what I [F#7]wanna see\n\n{c: CHORUS 3}\n\nDamn your [Bm7]eyes\nFor taking my [E9]breath away\nFor making me[Gmaj7] wanna st[F#7]ay\n[Bm7]Damn your eyes\n[E9]For getting my hopes up high\nFor making me [Em9]fall in love agai[F#7]n\n[Bm7]Damn your eyes   [E9]\n\n\n\nDamn yor eye[Bm7]s\nFor taking my br[E9]eath away\nDamn d[Bm7]amn your eyes\nFor getting my h[E9]opes up high\nFor making me [Bm7]fall in love\nFall in love a[E9]gain\nDamn damn your [Bm7]eyes  [E9]\n\n","hash":"27f4dee434ed334e25dd61c112ab48c9","key":5,"KeyShift":1,"name":"Damn Your Eyes","subTitle":"","type":1,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-08-26T19:54:57.953565Z","Deleted":false,"SyncId":"9a79d137-8462-4126-a014-b91bdb422584","timeSig":"","ZoomFactor":1.0,"Duration":0,"Duration2":0,"_displayParams":"{}","TempoInt":0,"_tags":"[]","Url":"","DeepSearch":"damn your eyes\netta james\ni can do what i want i'm in complete control\ndamn your eyes\ndye\n","Copyright":"","NotesText":"","Zoom":1.0,"SectionOrder":"","SongNumber":0,"HasChildren":0,"ParentId":0,"vName":null,"locked":0,"LinkedAudio":null,"Chords":null,"midiOnLoad":null,"_folders":"[]","drawingPathsBackup":null}],"sets":[{"details":{"Id":205,"name":"TestSet","date":"2025-09-01T04:40:47.559936Z","ModifiedDateTime":"2025-09-01T04:40:47.559960Z","Deleted":0,"SyncId":"548a6427-8e6a-4938-9cef-8dc40a36e8b6"},"contents":[{"Id":4221,"Order":0,"Capo":0,"SetId":205,"SongId":5,"keyOfset":0,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-09-01T04:40:47.559967Z","Deleted":0,"SyncId":"7911b996-24da-4b72-b6dc-140c480bb295","NotesText":null,"SectionOrder":"","ItemType":1,"Content":"","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":4222,"Order":1,"Capo":0,"SetId":205,"SongId":147,"keyOfset":0,"ModifiedDateTime":"2025-09-01T04:40:47.559973Z","Deleted":0,"SyncId":"616441bd-245e-4af3-8255-0fd43669f2a9","NotesText":null,"SectionOrder":"","ItemType":1,"Content":"","drawingPathsBackup":null},{"Id":42